巾清潔既習慣，即係代表佢已經慣左口部污糟既情況，懶得清理，呢個時候，你只要遞張前晚打完丁既紙巾比佢，佢就會明白你既意思</blockquote><br />\n好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9c6a18d829ad5d7af8336e4fe62d99598ed45b","tid":296944,"uid":23842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:03:53.000Z","msg":"你放d辣椒係鳩到佢含到你都痛死左啦"},{"pid":"4e5e0402413d6b37bde405c4b842bc6715255fb6","tid":296944,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:07:11.000Z","msg":"我識唔少女仔都用手抹咀喎<br />\n<br />\n咁咪全部都淫底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7542c920f49fa403f8e3a8d4a3daf32fdadd723a","tid":296944,"uid":24024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:12:11.000Z","msg":"幽默感真係無得勉強..."},{"pid":"4c0d9125ee64f8daff3ff8260c5f3a9706c0c583","tid":296944,"uid":123014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:13:46.000Z","msg":"氣場 未必著得暴露就淫底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d924654afeba11a831b49b4b3c5273b4a2ef0a23","tid":296944,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:16:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你放d辣椒係鳩到佢含到你都痛死左啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2365cba4aa7491eee43b058d5e1521d36e301e9","tid":296944,"uid":68547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:16:51.000Z","msg":"腿露的比例"},{"pid":"dd00b6da81fec1732fee7a0c0d6b2e9f437f1f56","tid":296944,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:17:23.000Z","msg":"新潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae34765e5218e0503d7ed7adcbc2f9e7283c6d4","tid":296944,"uid":15381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:36:23.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"9c307e9f3d133c0911045a7d775c7cdb25cade48","tid":